Format and Naming 
  Scheme

The naming scheme for your 
    homework in electronic version: BM2006HWNOID.DOC
    where NO denotes the number of HW, and ID denotes your student ID. For 
    example, your ID is B86106055 and the work is the second HW. 
    Therefore, the name for your work should be BM2006HW02B86106055.DOC.

    　

