資訊機構管理領域
謝寶煖



透過本課程的學習，同學可以： 瞭解服務管理與行銷的重要管理職能、瞭解如何設計服務產品與管理服提供過程、有效掌握改善服務品質與價值的方法、建立顧客導向的服務哲學。





LIS5057
圖書館作業評估
3
學士班/碩士班
選修
資訊機構管理領域
唐牧群
連結







LIS5057
圖書館作業評估
3
學士班/碩士班
選修
資訊機構管理領域
唐牧群



This class examines goals, criteria, measures, measuring instruments and methods of evaluating a variety of library and information services. Emphasis is placed on the use of data for planning and decision making purpose. Topics covered include evaluation of collection, applied bibliometrics, availability analysis, usability test and online information retrieval evaluation. Methods surveyed include circulation and log analyses, experimental design, protocol analysis, focus group and survey. 





