黃慕萱



This course attempts to broaden an overview of the subject, touching upon all-important areas; hopefully this will encourage some of you to pursue certain areas in more detail through further reading and/or your own research. This course covers three subjects: (a) Bibliometrics (b) Patentometrics (Patent Bibliometrics) (c) Webometrics (Cybermetrics)





